column.name: htmlheader
column.value:
<style type="text/css">

	.hidden{
		position:absolute;
		left:-10000px;
		top:auto;
		width:1px;
		height:1px;
		overflow:hidden;
}

	.alignleft{
		float:left;
}

	.alignright{
		float:right;
		text-align:right;
}

	.clearalign{
		clear:both;
}

	.templatedesign01 {
		background:#f4eece;    	/* Top background colour */
}

	#maincontentbox {
		padding-top:8px;
}

	.left_centre_right .colleft, .left_centre{
		background:#dab366;    	/* Left column background colour */
}


	#wrapper_outer, #maincontentbox, .centre, .centre_right, .centre_right .colleft, .left_centre .colright, .left_centre_right, .left_centre_right .colmid, .left_right, .left_right .colleft{
		background-color:#faf5ea;    	/* Content background colour */
}


/* Needed to expand width for ecommerce toolbar */
	#wrapper_outer{
	   /* YOU CAN USE px, em OR % */
		width:1060px;               
}


	#wrapper_inner{
		padding:0 35px;
}


</style>
